name: Who is The Real King?
description: It doesn't meant to offend anyone. Everything is about a symbol. Chicken is just my symbol for myself and my Personality. In this world, there are always those who are stronger than the strong. And always beat the weak. The economic in the world that happened since ancient times has also been like that. But, is the strong always be bad? Or, the bad forever as wicked? They are also hesitated. Because there is always an opportunity to be better as long as you are alive.
